{"tid":1599643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎緊既選舉劇本會係咁寫...............","createTime":"2019-09-28T06:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T07:10:59.000Z","uid":112748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e327c085f2bfbe1cacca527fb3439a74d18862","tid":1599643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">黎緊既選舉，政府為左保住保共派，會有兩個步署必然好大機會出現，<span style=\"color: red;\">1</span>.先派出大量掌心雷、蛇齋餅受益隊伍等、短時間內湧入票站，推高有利票數，<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>. 如前者效果不理想，就直接關閉投票中心，該選區繼續由上屆議員繼續參與議會工作，直到&quot;適當&quot;時候重新補選.............而可以使到前兩者&quot;合理&quot;化，必然會係該選區票站，上演一場民鬥民既沖突事件，然後快速公布關閉票站、截止投票！<br />\n今日林奠同班保共派開會，事先張楊地公布左真係會咁做，大家覺得係咪又眼白白比佢地照住呢個劇本走？有無對策？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"86e6153dce4eaab9d8125a16a530a1f3f93c81fd","tid":1599643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cb92c2b89a6098a31cc1aa13653a96324ee2db","tid":1599643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0f46f1c9e06421bf47de073ee4d7ab208e6694","tid":1599643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1580c8c81dc49c1d2e9317fc8d954664dfd8a10","tid":1599643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644a0c1231c1